Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:43.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（不動(ふどう) 明(あきら)）\N違う！ 俺は悪魔なんかじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.48,0:01:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm not a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:45.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（銃声）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:50.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（明）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:54.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ミーコ）はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:58.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガビ）ヒエ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.74,0:01:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:04.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は悪魔じゃない…\N人間 不動 明だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Akira Fudo. A human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:11.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ミーコ）んっ…\N（明）美樹(みき)！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:14.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ワム）来るな 牧村(まきむら)！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stay back, Makimura.\N-Trust me, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:16.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信じてくれ 美樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:20.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はずっと…\Nずっと悪魔と戦ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been fighting against\Nthe demons this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:25.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間を守るために……\N悪魔になった この体を使って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To protect the humans,\NI've been using my body
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that merged with a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:26.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガビ）ほら 悪魔だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-See, he's a devil.\N-Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:29.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信じてくれ！\N心は人間のままなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-I still have the heart of a human.\N-Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:31.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ワム）ふざけんじゃねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'd kill a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:33.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（明）人を殺すなんてありえない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:37.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは俺じゃないはずだ！\N俺が人を殺すなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never kill a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:38.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガビ）確証ないのか\N（明）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:41.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガビ）\Nだから牧村にも秘密だったんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you\Nkept it from Makimura, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:43.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（明）んっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ワム）おい 近づくな 牧村！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't go near him, Makimura.\N-He's a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:51.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガビ）そいつは悪魔だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:54.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（牧村美樹）あの時もそうだった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the same back then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:03:01.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明君 さっきも\N家族のために泣いてくれたよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira, you were crying\Nfor my family earlier, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:06.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は… あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:13.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明君は変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:17.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう 美樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We are family, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:21.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だって家族だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:25.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガビ）はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:27.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:34.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（パトカーのサイレン）\N（明）あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ミーコ）来た！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:38.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガビ）ん… はえーな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You, get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:40.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は出てけ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:43.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼んだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:48.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は了(りょう)に会わなければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go meet Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明君 でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:52.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず美樹の元へ戻る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come back to you, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:04:00.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ… 約束だぞ\N君がアンカーだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:04:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a promise.\NYou are the anchor, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:02.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:07.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（警察無線）不動明を牧村邸で確認\N近隣住民から通報あり
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We received a tip that\N{\i1}Akira Fudo's at the Makimura residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:09.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,応援送れ！ 相手は悪魔だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We need backup.\N{\i1}This is a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:16.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（警官１）\N牧村一家 不動明を出せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Makimura family, give us Akira Fudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:17.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かくまっても無駄だぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:18.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（警官２）悪魔だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-A devil!\N-There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:19.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（警官３）出たぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:20.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（警官３）出たぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:20.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（銃声）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（銃声）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:22.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（銃声）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:22.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（警官４）追え！ 逃がすな！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:23.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（警官４）追え！ 逃がすな！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,GO TO HELL, YOU MORTALS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:40.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（スタッフ）はい カット！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And, cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are weak\Nwhen it comes to authorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:45.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雷沼(らいぬま)デーモン）人間というヤツは\N権威に弱いから―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:47.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今のデマを信じるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll believe the lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:50.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（デーモンたちの笑い声）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:54.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゼイ）どちらへ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where to?\N-Back to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:56.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（飛鳥(あすか) 了）マンションに戻る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:05:00.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで明は\N私の所へ来るしかなくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Akira doesn't have a choice\Nbut to come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:01.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,幸田(こうだ)！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Koda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（デビルマン）\Nなぜだ… なぜだ 了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, Ryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆１）おら この野郎！\N（民衆２）撃っちまえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-You fool!\N-Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hurry up!\N-Die! You devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:11.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆３）早く死ね！\N（民衆４）死ねー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:14.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆５）悪魔め！\N（民衆６）パパを返せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-Daddy!\N-Give me my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Devil!\N-Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:17.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆の怒声）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:20.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（デビルマン）やめろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:23.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（眼鏡）ひゃああ\N（民衆８）悪魔だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-A devil.\N-Are you on his side?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:26.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆９）かばう気だ\N（民衆10）助けに来た
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-He's come to save them.\N-The guy from TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（眼鏡）テレビのヤツだ\N（民衆12）テレビで見たぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:29.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆13）警察 呼べ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-Call the police!\N-It's Akira Fudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:30.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆14）不動明だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:32.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:38.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はデビルマンだが\Nこいつらは ただの人間だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Devilman,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're just humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:41.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間が人間を殺すのか！ くっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you humans gonna kill other humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kill him!\N-Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:43.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆の怒声）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:45.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいかげんにしろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:51.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつらが本当に悪魔だったら\Nお前らなんか一撃で殺せるんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If they were really demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd all be killed in one blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:59.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 車 取り行ってっから\N戻ったら すぐここを離れる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting in the car right now.\NWe'll leave as soon as it gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:03.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人殺しはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:05.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:10.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ これもらっといてくれ\N（美樹）ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then hold on to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:14.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ワム）ヒーローのお守りだ\N世話になった人にもらったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll protect you. It's from someone\Nwho looked after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:15.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Do you think it'll work?\N-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:19.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,効くかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:20.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無敵さ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I wish I could have lent it to Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:25.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなら 明君に\N貸してあげたかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:29.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か二度と会えないような\N気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'll never see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:36.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたらしくねえな\N信じろ あいつのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And believe in that bling, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:38.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのピアスの力も
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-Try killing me!\N-Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:40.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆１）殺してみろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆２）死ね！\N（眼鏡）人間なめんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-Your time is over!\N-I won't kill humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:44.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人は殺さない\N俺も人間だからだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm also a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:46.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆３）殺してたろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（銃声）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:48.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（デビルマン）うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:52.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人を… 人を殺すなー！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! Don't kill humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆たち）わあっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:57.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は… 俺の心は人間なんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the heart of a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are humans fighting one another?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:02.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で人間同士でいがみ合う！\N殺し合うんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why kill each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to kill, kill a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:06.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殺すなら悪魔を殺せ！\N俺を殺せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you kill each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:11.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で殺し合う！\N憎しみ合うんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you hate each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆４）何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Is he crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:17.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆５）泣いてんのか？\N（民衆６）痛かったか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-Did it hurt?\N-He cried. He cried!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:19.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（眼鏡）泣いた 泣いたよ\N（民衆７）ハハッ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-Strange fluid's coming out of his eyes.\N-Do devils have hearts, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆８）泣いてんのか\N（民衆９）目から変な汁出た
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:23.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔にも心があんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't be fooled.\N-He's a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:25.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆10）だまされんな\N（民衆11）こいつ悪魔だぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:29.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆の怒声）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today I would like\N{\i1}to talk about someone important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akira Fudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A lot of you probably just saw him on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akira said he's not a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is a Devilman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has the body of a demon,\N{\i1}but the heart of a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think his heart hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He cries for other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's always been like that,\N{\i1}since he was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He cried for me when I couldn't cry\N{\i1}because I was being stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When Akira cries,\N{\i1}it's always for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He doesn't cry at all\N{\i1}when he's sad himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has a strong heart.\N{\i1}But he mostly cries for other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:08.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆１）悪魔 死ねー！\N（民衆２）人間なめんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If more people\N{\i1}in the world were like Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think everyone would be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crying for other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and thinking about other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That might just be a fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...if it's a person\N{\i1}with a heart like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}whether they are demon or human...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll accept them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And love them unconditionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:47.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Peace will come if everyone believes that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I'm powerless on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if each of us is powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we all believed that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the world would change in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:18.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“私もデビルマンです”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:20.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:26.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆１）おい あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:29.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆２）\Nやめろ そいつは悪魔だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop. He's a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:31.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:36.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“あなたの勇気に\N敬意を表します”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Devilman my ass\NMust have a death wish
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:45.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆３）おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:47.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆４）あれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:51.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,んっ ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,FOUND A DEVIL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,SAME PERSON?\NCHECK THE IP ADDRESS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:06.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆５）だまされるか！\N（民衆６）悪魔め！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be fooled. You devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆７）バカ こっち来い！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! Traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:10.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆８）裏切り者だ！\Nもろとも殺せー！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,DIE! LIAR!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'M ALSO A DEVILMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'M A DEVILMAN TOO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,HUMAN HEARTS ARE EQUAL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,THERE'S NO HUMAN?\NI WANT TO BELIEVE TOO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I TOLD MY WIFE I'M A DEVILMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I will believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:40.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男１）信じるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:44.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（女１）ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:47.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（女２）ごめんなさいね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:50.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい\N（男２）悪かった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:51.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（女３）ごめんね\N（男３）すまん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（女４）うう… うう…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:55.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男４）おい\N（男５）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男４）ほら\N（男６）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:05.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（了）ふっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Devilman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:07.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（幸田）よう デビルマン
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:10.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（幸田マン）うああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:13.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民衆のざわめき）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The world belongs to the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:15.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界は悪魔のものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:18.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（デビルマン）ぐおわああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:19.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（幸田マン）ガアア！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Koda.\NMove, we'll finish it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:22.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（デーモン）よくやった幸田\Nどいてろ とどめだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:24.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろー！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:31.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:33.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（幸田マン）チッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:40.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（デビルマン）ううっ…\N（デーモン）ウガッ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:43.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガアア
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:45.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウガー！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:53.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（デビルマン）ううっ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:00.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゼノン）ガァハ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（デビルマン）ぐうっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:10.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわああ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:15.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゼノン）ぶあ… ぐあ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うがああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:20.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おああああー
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:21.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（デビルマン）うううう！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:24.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゼノン）があああ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the holdup?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:39.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おせえな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,DEVILMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to beat you\Nin track-and-field,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:46.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ミーコ）陸上で―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:49.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,美樹に勝ちたかったけど\Nかなわなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was never able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:52.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（美樹）また次の機会あるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:57.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっと… 美樹のこと嫌いだった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,hated you, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:58.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:02.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ミーコ）ずっと１番だった\N私の立場 奪った
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always the best,\Nbut you took that away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:04.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私もミキなのに―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm Miki,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:10.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたと一緒にいたら\Nミーコって呼ばれるようになった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,people started to call me Miko around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:11.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（美樹）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:15.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取材もいっぱい来た\N“美樹ちゃんの友達ですか？”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I got asked in a lot of interviews\Nif I was your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:18.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“美樹ちゃんのこと\N教えてください”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They wanted me to tell them about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:20.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“美樹ちゃんはどう思うかな？”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,About what you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're beautiful, popular, fashionable,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:24.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,美人で人気者でセンスよくて\Nいいヤツで何でも１番
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and the best at everything.\NAlways the best. I hated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:29.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１番１番… ホント ヤなヤツ\Nホント 大っ嫌いだった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I seriously hated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:34.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:40.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも… 大好きだった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:42.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それも知ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:46.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私… ずっと分からなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:50.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ミーコ 今かっこいい\N前のミーコも好きだったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Miko, you're so cool now.\NBut I liked you how you were before, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ミーコ）ごめん…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガラスが割れる音）\N（美樹）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:58.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒１）牧村美樹の家だ！\N（暴徒２）悪魔の家！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:15:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Miki Makimura's house!\NWitch's house! Devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒３）\N悪魔！ 不動明をかくまっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガラスが割れる音）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-Get weapons.\N-They're from the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:03.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,牧村 武器を用意しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:04.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,近所の人たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:08.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ターコ）ギャオ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:09.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（美樹）ターコ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つきあいは\N賞味期限切れらしいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Relationships don't last forever.\NGo upstairs. I'll stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:13.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３階へ逃げろ！ 食い止める
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:16.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ドアをたたく音）\N（暴徒１）いたぞっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:18.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ワム）おらっ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガビ）クッ… クッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:22.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ワム）うう… ううう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:24.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ワム･ガビ）うおっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:27.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒２）うひゃひゃ… あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:30.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あああ… うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:33.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒３）へへへ\N（ガビ）入ってくんな こら！ おら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:35.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ワム）ぬう…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wamu!\N-Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:40.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ワム！\N（ミーコ）美樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:42.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガラスが割れる音）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（美樹）死ぬなよ ヒーロー！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die, hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Get outside if you want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死にたくねえヤツは\N外に出ろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:56.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（明）美樹！ 戻るよ 君の所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:16:00.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は君から\N一番 大切なものを受け取った
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:16:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the most important thing\Nof all from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:04.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が人間であり続けるのは\N君がいるからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can remain a human because you exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒１）くっ 魔女め！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:13.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（美樹）えいっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:19.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒２）魔女いたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's that witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:20.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒３）外人め！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-You outsider.\N-That's right. I'm different from you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:23.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうよ あんたたちとは違う
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:24.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒４）魔女め\N（美樹）私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-You witch!\N-I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-Witch!\N-A witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:26.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒５）魔女！\N（美樹）魔女よ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:27.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒６）わあー！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:28.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒６）わあ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:35.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒７）魔女だ！\N（暴徒８）魔女 屋根に逃げたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's that witch!\N-She's on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:37.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（美樹）ミーコ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Miko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:43.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ミーコ）ごめん 私の背中\N乗ってくれる？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Will you ride on my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:46.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうするの？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:48.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ミーコ）飛ぶ！\N（美樹）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-By the river!\N-Follow them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:57.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒９）逃げた！\N（暴徒10）河原のほうだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:16:58.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒11）追え！\N（暴徒12）逃げたぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:05.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒12）おおっ\N（暴徒13）なんだこいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:06.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ターコ）ニャー！\N（暴徒たち）うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:10.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガビ）ッツ… 邪魔すんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:13.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,う～ おっ！ おわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:17.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒）てめ…\N（ガビ）ふんっ！ はあ はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へっ どうしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:29.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… う…\N（暴徒）へっへっへ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:32.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガビ）なんで… ぐがっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:34.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒）ひゃっほー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing I want to protect\Nthe most is you, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:38.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（明）俺が一番 守りたいもの\Nそれは美樹 君だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:41.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ってろ！ 今 行く！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on. I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:48.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明のヤツ… 遅いな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira's taking a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:59.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ミーコ）ここ よく走ったね\Nいっつも走ってたね！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to run here often, didn't we?\NWe were always running.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（美樹）よく練習した！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We practiced a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to always chase after you.\NYou were good at everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:06.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ミーコ）私は何でもできる\Nあんたをいつも追いかけてた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:10.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 あんた大好きだから！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:11.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私もー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:12.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（銃声）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Miko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:13.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（美樹）ミーコ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:15.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ミーコ）走るの好き！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I love running!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:18.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（美樹）私も好き！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I love running, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:20.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ミーコ）走れてよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:21.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（銃声）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:25.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐっ… ん… ミーコ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Miko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:27.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ミーコ）美樹 走れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:30.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,走れ 美樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:33.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,走れ 美樹ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:39.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,美樹ー！ ファイトー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Miko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ミーコ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:47.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒１）おぞましいな\N（暴徒２）悪魔め
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Disgusting.\N-You devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where's the witch?\N-Is she running?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:49.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒３）魔女は？\N（暴徒４）走ってんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:55.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたたちに問う
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:57.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒１）何だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:19:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean to be human?\NWhat does it mean to be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:19:01.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間らしくあることとは！\N善良であることとは！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:03.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒５）死ぬなら早く死ねよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-If you're gonna die, hurry up.\N-What is justice? What is right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正義とは！ 正しいこととは！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:08.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒３）悪魔は死ぬべきだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Devils should die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:09.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,牧村美樹を助けて！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Save Miki Makimura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒３）死ねよ 早く
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hurry up and die.\N-Die already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:12.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（暴徒４）早く死ね！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let her live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:14.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願い！ 彼女を生かして
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:15.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:17.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（銃声）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:07.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（美樹）\N何で走るのか？\N理屈は分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do I run?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just like to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:13.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,好きだから… ちょっとでも\Nほんの少しでも前へ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even just a little,\N{\i1}just a tiny bit farther.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I go forward,\N{\i1}I feel like something will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:17.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前へ進めば\N何かが変わる気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:21.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取るに足らない\Nほんの少しでも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's trivial.\N{\i1}Even if it's just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even just a little.\N{\i1}Even the smallest bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:24.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっとでも\Nほんのちょっとでも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:26.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（荒い息）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:30.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（銃声）\Nぐっ… はあ はあ はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira! I have to pass you the baton!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:34.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明君！ あなたに\Nバトン渡さなきゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:39.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（美樹の荒い息）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:42.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ… ワム！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:45.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:49.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ… は…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.46,0:20:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:56.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（中学生の美樹）\N明君… バトン… 明君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The baton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The baton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:57.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（美樹）バトン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:13.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぎやあああああああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,美樹 戻ってきたよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki, I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:18.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,美樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:57.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（デビルマン）はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:24.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は… は… はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.68,0:22:31.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… ああ… ああああ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.06,0:22:39.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… ぐう… うああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are the ones who are demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.36,0:22:44.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔だ… お前たちこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.24,0:22:47.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地獄へ落ちろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:52.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間どもめー！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.58,0:22:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you mortals!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.13,0:27:14.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,&lrm;日本語字幕　後藤 太郎
